    "body": "> Please be carefull with asterisk(star) “*” - shell may replace it with files list.\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/65291464/175803639-622c30af-e22d-45f4-8e93-03d36ca03292.png)\r\nI remove it!\r\n\r\n`--rpc.accessList`   overrides the parameter `--http.api`. \r\nIf I want to enable `eth_newBlockFilter, eth_newPendingTransactionFilter, eth_newFilter, eth_getFilterChanges` , I must add  all `eth_* net_* web3_*  ......`  methods into the rules.json.  Unfriendly!\r\nHow about you opinion?",
