    "author_association": "COLLABORATOR",
    "body": "when you use --rpc.accessList, you need to specify *ALL* individual methods in the rules.json file. I know that because I use the same configuration, both params work together (\"AND\").\r\n\r\nSo, --http.api means \"you are allowed to use those namespaces\", but specifying --rpc.accessList reset all allowances.  But specifying only --rpc.accessList is not enough, but need to specify the methods AND enable the namespaces in --http.api.",
